INSERT INTO `mice` VALUES ('10146684','Logitech Wireless Laser Mouse X','19.99','With its contoured design and plug-and-forget nano-receiver, the Logitech Wireless Mouse M310 is the easy-to-use, full-size mouse that feels just right. Plus, it gives you the freedom of wireless, so you can work and play with ease no matter where you are.','<ul><li>Enjoy smooth, responsive cursor control on a variety of surfaces, easy text selection, and effortless scrolling</li><li>It feels good in either hand - even after long hours of use - thanks to its hand-friendly, contoured design with soft rubber side grips</li><li>The plug-and-forget nano-receiver is so small it stays in your USB port so you won\'t lose it, or you can store it inside the mouse</li><li>Enjoy a reliable wireless connection with virtually no delays or dropouts with the advanced 2.4 GHz connectivity</li><li>Stay productive for up to 12 months without battery hassles (may vary depending on usage)</li><li>An on/off switch helps conserve power</li><li>A smart sleep mode extends battery life</li><li>Indicator light</li></ul>'),('10147869','Logitech Wireless Laser Mouse','34.98','With its contoured shape, soft rubber grips and handy controls, the Logitech Wireless Mouse M510 gives you more control, so you can work and play in total comfort.','<ul><li>Flip through photo albums and web pages using the three standard buttons plus back/forward buttons that you can program to switch applications, go full screen and more</li><li>Side-to-side scrolling plus zoom gives you the power to scroll horizontally and vertically through your content</li><li>Enjoy the freedom of wireless with no cables to restrict your movement or worry about</li><li>The Logitech Unifying receiver is small enough to stay in your computer or laptop</li></ul>'),('10398045','Apple Magic Mouse 2 - Satin White','99.99','Redesigned, rechargeable, remarkable. That\'s Apple accessories for you, and the Magic Mouse 2 is no different. Its lightweight, streamlined design allows it to track easier and move with less resistance, while the Multi-Touch surface lets you perform simple gestures such as swiping between web pages and scrolling through documents.','<ul><li>This redesigned wireless mouse is ready to go right out of the box and pairs automatically with your Mac via Bluetooth</li><li>Features a built-in rechargeable battery so youâ€™ll eliminate the use of traditional batteries</li><li>Lightweight construction, optimized foot design, and fewer moving parts (thanks to its built-in battery and continuous bottom shell) make for more effortless tracking and smoother, more fluid movement across surfaces</li><li>Multi-Touch surface offers the freedom to perform simple gestures such as swiping between web pages and scrolling through documents</li></ul>'),('10406371','Logitech G502 Wired Optical Gaming Mouse','74.99','Make the Logitech G502 Proteus Spectrum gaming mouse your weapon of choice for PC gaming. It features G Delta Zero optical sensor tech that delivers up to 12000 DPI for exceptionally accurate tracking. Five included tuning weights lets you control the weight and balance, and 11 programmable buttons put your macros and commands at your fingertips.','<ul><li>Gaming mouse with right-hand design</li><li>G Delta Zero optical sensor technology (200 to 12000 DPI) delivers incredible tracking accuracy</li><li>Customizable RGB lighting lets you choose from 16.8 million colours to match your unique style</li><li>Tweak the weight for the ideal balance with the 5 included 3.6g weights</li><li>11 programmable buttons put your favourite macros and in-game commands at your fingertips and save up to 3 onboard profiles</li><li>Optional Proteus Spectrum Logitech gaming software (requires internet connection and 100MB of HDD space) allows you to tune the sensor to match your playing surface to maximize performance</li><li>Textured rubber grips offer a comfortable user experience</li></ul>'),('10482681','Logitech M720 Triathlon Wireless Optical Mouse','49.99','Built for endurance Logitech M720 Triathlon wireless optical mouse gives you 24 months of use on a single AA battery. Plus, the buttons are designed to withstand up to 10 million clicks. Easy-Switch technology allows you to use the mouse with up to 3 different computers. It\'s equipped with a hyper-fast scroll wheel that lets you fly through pages.','<ul><li>Built for endurance, versatility, and comfort, the M720 Triathlon Mouse lets you switch </li><li>Share the M720 Triathlon between 3 computers with Easy-Switch technology</li><li>A hyper-fast scroll wheel lets you fly through documents and web pages and shift to click-to-click scrolling offer precision when you need it</li><li>Buttons are designed to withstand up to 10 million clicks</li><li>Get up to 24 months of use on a single AA battery</li><li>Logitech Options software unlocks a full range of customizable settings, allowing you to tailor the M720 to fit your needs on Mac OS X and Windows</li></ul>'),('10508982','Corsair M65 PRO RGB 12000 DPI','64.99','The Corsair Gaming M65 Pro RGB gaming mouse is built to meet the uncompromising needs of first-person shooter competitors and other hardcore gamers. It features a rubber-molded metal high-mass scroll wheel, dedicated sniper button, 8 programmable buttons, adjustable weight-tuning zones, a 12,000 DPI laser sensor, and more.','<ul><li>Aircraft-grade all-aluminum construction means the mouse is low weight, has high rigidity, and offers optimal mass distribution</li><li>12,000 DPI high-accuracy laser sensor delivers quick, responsive, intelligent, and pixel-precise control</li><li>On-the-fly DPI switching lets you instantly match mouse speed to gameplay demands as they develop </li><li>Surface calibration tuning utility allows you to optimize the sensor based on your playing surface </li><li>Features 8 programmable buttons are fully configurable for personalized play</li><li>High-mass scroll wheel with metal interior, rubberized exterior for tremendous tactile precision</li><li>Optimized sniper button positioning for accuracy in first-person shooters</li><li>Engineered to endure over extended play with high-capacity Omron switches rated for 20 million clicks</li><li>Advanced centre of gravity weight tuning zones adds stability that balances your natural</li></ul>'),('10752498','Logitech MX Anywhere 2S Bluetooth Mouse','73.98','When your professional priorities hover somewhere between productivity and portability, the Logitech MX Anywhere 2S is here to help. Hand-sculpted for comfort, this Bluetooth-enabled mouse charges quickly and boasts a premium 4000 DPI Darkfield sensor for precise tracking on almost any surface. And its compact design fits easily in any pocket.','<ul><li>4000 DPI Darkfield sensor provides you with impeccable control on practically anything, from a glass table to a high-gloss surface (4mm minimum thickness)</li><li>Precision wheel auto-shifts from click-to-click so you can scroll through web pages more quickly for a super enjoyable navigation experience</li><li>Enjoy fine-motion control and fluid experience with well-positioned buttons and wheels</li><li>Logitech FLOW technology lets you seamlessly control up to 3 computers with one mouse and even copy-paste text, images, and files between them</li><li>Power your mouse for a full day\'s work in just 3 minutes, and enjoy up to 70 days battery life on a full charge</li><li>Mobile design is made to stash easily in any pocket</li></ul>'),('10752528','Logitech MX Master 2S Bluetooth Mouse','87.98','Powerful productivity in the palm of your hand, the MX Master 2S wireless mouse helps you do more. Its speed adaptive scroll wheel auto-shifts from click-to-click to hyper-fast scroll, so you can navigate large web pages and documents quickly and easily. And amazing FLOW technology lets you seamlessly manage your workflow between multiple computers.','<ul><li>4000 DPI Darkfield high precision sensor provides you with impeccable control on practically anything, from a glass table to a high-gloss surface (4mm minimum thickness)</li><li>Smart speed-adaptive scroll wheel allows for fast scrolling through long documents and webpages and auto-shifts from click-to-click to hyper-fast scroll</li><li>Enjoy intuitive side-to-side scrolling with a stroke of your thumb</li><li>Logitech FLOW technology lets you seamlessly control up to 3 computers with one mouse and copy-paste text, images and files between them</li><li>Power your mouse for a full day\'s work in just 3 minutes, and enjoy up to 70 days battery life on a full charge</li><li>Hand-sculpted contour supports your hand and wrist comfortably and is easy to grip </li><li>Enjoy fine-motion control and a fluid experience with the well-positioned buttons and wheels</li></ul>'),('10846740','Microsoft Surface Arc Mouse - Black','59.99','Slim, lightweight, and ready to travel, the Microsoft Surface Arc Mouse blends modern style and form with intuitive function and feel. The curved design means the mouse fits comfortably and in your hand and makes a sleek addition to any work space. Bluetooth connectivity frees you from cable clutter, while the snap-flat feature lets you pack it and go.','<ul><li>Ultra-thin and ultra-lightweight wireless mouse is designed to conform to the natural curvature of your hand for enhanced all-day comfort</li><li>Clean, elegant, and minimalist style looks great in any workspace and is designed to complement your other Microsoft Surface devices (sold separately)</li><li>Built-in Bluetooth 4.0 technology allows for a quick and easy wireless connection to avoid the hassle of dealing with cables</li><li>Innovative design allows the mouse to snapped flat and easily tucked into a laptop back or backpack for on-the-go convenience while you travel</li><li>When snapped into a curved position the mouse powers on for use; when snapped flat the mouse powers down to conserve battery life</li><li>Full-scroll plane on the top of the mouse lets you scroll both vertically and horizontally</li><li>Compatible with Microsoft Windows 10, Windows 8.1, and Windows 8 operating systems</li></ul>'),('11622659','Logitech MX Master Bluetooth Laser Mouse','69.99','Streamline your workflow and minimize cord clutter in your workspace with this Logitech MX Master wireless mouse. Equipped with Darkfield High Precision tracking technology, this mouse can be used on just about any surface, including glass. It also features 7 different programmable buttons and all-day battery life.','<ul><li>Bluetooth wireless mouse with 1000dpi sensitivity is designed for power users and multitaskers</li><li>Darkfield High Precision tracking technology means this mouse can be used on just about any surface, even glass (with a 4mm minimum thickness)</li><li>Hand-sculpted shape supports your hand and wrist in a comfortable, natural position for all-day usage</li><li>Built-in rechargeable battery offers all-day battery life after approximately 3 minutes of charging time; battery can be charged using an included micro-USB cable</li><li>Features 7 different buttons that can be assigned specific tasks and shortcuts, to help you increase your productivity</li><li>Speed-adaptive scroll wheel auto-shifts from click-to-click to hyper-fast scroll and side-to-side scrolling with a stroke of your thumb</li></ul>');
